msgid "Single Sampling Plan"
msgstr "Satu Rencana Pensampelan"

msgid "Multiple Sampling Plan"
msgstr "Beberapa Rencana Pensampelan"

msgid "Acceptance Sampling Plan"
msgstr "Rencana Pensampelan Penerimaan"

msgid "Value"
msgstr "Nilai"

msgid "Sample"
msgstr "Sampel"

msgid "Sample Size"
msgstr "Ukuran Sampel"

msgid "Cum. Sample Size"
msgstr "Ukuran Sampel Kum."

msgid "Acc. Number"
msgstr "Angka Prm."

msgid "Rej. Number"
msgstr "Angka Plk."

msgid "Analyze Variable Plan"
msgstr "Analisis Rencana Variabel"

msgid "Variable Sampling Plan (Standard deviation assumed to be <b>%s</b>)"
msgstr "Rencana Pensampelan Variabel (Deviasi Standar diasumsi <b>%s</b>)"

msgid "Sample size"
msgstr "Ukuran sampel"

msgid "Critical Distance (k)"
msgstr "Jarak Kritis (k)"

msgid "If historical standard deviation is unknown, sample size has to be > 1."
msgstr "Jika deviasi standar historik tidak diketahui, ukuran sampel harus > 1."

msgid "Lot size (N = %1$.0f) cannot be smaller than the sample size (n = %2$.0f) of the generated variable plan."
msgstr ""
"Ukuran lot (N = %1$.0f) tidak dapat lebih kecil dari ukuran sampel (n = "
"%2$.0f) rencana variabel terhasilkan."

msgid "Lower limit for proportion non-conforming items needs to be smaller than the upper limit."
msgstr ""
"Batas bawah untuk item non-konform proporsi perlu lebih kecil dari batas "
"atas."

msgid "Step size for proportion non-conforming items needs to be smaller than the difference between the upper and lower limits."
msgstr ""
"Ukuran langkah untuk item non-konform proporsi perlu lebih kecil dari "
"perbedaan antara batas atas dan bawah."

msgid "Step size of 0 is allowed only if the lower and upper limits of proportion non-conforming items are identical."
msgstr ""
"Ukuran langkah 0 diizinkan hanya jika batas bawah dan atas item non-konform "
"proporsi identik."

msgid "For hypergeometric distribution, N * proportion non-conforming should all be integer values.\n\nCheck the values of N and proportion non-conforming."
msgstr ""
"Untuk distribusi hipergeometris, N * non-konform proporsi harus semua nilai "
"integer.\n"
"\n"
"Periksa nilai N dan non-konform proporsi."

msgid "Sample size (n) cannot be larger than the lot size (N)."
msgstr "Ukuran sampel (n) tidak dapat lebih besar dari ukuran lot (N)."

msgid "Acceptance number (c) cannot be larger than the sample size (n)."
msgstr "Angka penerimaan (c) tidak dapat lebih besar dari ukuran sampel (n)."

msgid "Rejection number (r) cannot be larger than the sample size (n)."
msgstr "Angka penolakan (r) tidak dapat lebih besar dari ukuran sampel (n)."

msgid "Rejection number (r) has to be larger than the acceptance number (c)."
msgstr "Angka penolakan (r) harus lebih besar dari angka penerimaan (c)."

msgid "Cumulative sample size (n1+n2+...) cannot be larger than the lot size (N)."
msgstr ""
"Ukuran sampel kumulatif (n1+n2+...) tidak dapat lebih besar dari ukuran lot "
"(N)."

msgid "Final rejection number (r) needs to be 1 more than the final acceptance number (c)."
msgstr ""
"Angka penolakan akhir (r) harus 1 lebih dari angka penerimaan akhir (c)."

msgid "Rejection number (r) for every stage has to be larger than the corresponding acceptance number (c)."
msgstr ""
"Angka penolakan (r) untuk setiap tahap harus lebih besar dari angka "
"penerimaan yang sesuai (c)."

msgid "For all stages except the last stage, rejection numbers (r) have to be at at least 2 greater than the acceptance numbers (c).\n\n                                   Else, subsequent stages become redundant."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua tahap kecuali tahap terakhir, angka penolakan (r) harus "
"setidaknya 2 lebih dari angka penerimaan (c).\n"
"\n"
"                                   Tidak, tahap subsekuen menjadi rendundan."

msgid "Acceptance numbers (c) are cumulative, so they need to be in a non-decreasing sequence."
msgstr ""
"Angka penerimaan (c) kumulatif, jadi mereka harus dalam sekuens non-"
"penurunan."

msgid "Rejection numbers (r) are cumulative, so they need to be in a non-decreasing sequence."
msgstr ""
"Angka penolakan (r) kumulatif, jadi mereka harus dalam sekuens non-penurunan."

msgid "No valid values found in the plan. Check the inputs."
msgstr "Tidak ada nilai valid ditemukan di rencana. Periksa masukan."

msgid "AQL (Acceptable Quality Level) value should be lower than RQL (Rejectable Quality Level) value."
msgstr ""
"Nilai AQL (Tingkat Kualitas Diterima) harus bawah dari nilai RQL (Tingkat "
"Kualitas Ditolak)."

msgid "1 - α (Producer's risk) has to be greater than β (consumer's risk)."
msgstr "1 - α (Risiko produsen) harus lebih dari β (risiko konsumen)."

msgid "Current plan <b>CAN %s</b> meet the specified risk point(s)."
msgstr "Rencana saat ini <b>DAPAT %s</b> memenuhi titik risiko tertentu."

msgid "Proportion Non-conforming"
msgstr "Non-konform Proporsi"

msgid "Required P(accept)"
msgstr "Diperlukan P(terima)"

msgid "Actual P(accept)"
msgstr "Aktual P(terima)"

msgid "Probability of acceptance (%1$.3f) at AQL (%2$.3f) is <b>lower</b> than the required probability of acceptance (%3$.3f) at AQL."
msgstr ""
"Probabilitas penerimaan (%1$.3f) di AQL (%2$.3f) <b>lebih rendah</b> dari "
"probabilitas penerimaan diperlukan (%3$.3f) di AQL."

msgid "Probability of acceptance (%1$.3f) at RQL (%2$.3f) is <b>higher</b> than the required probability of acceptance (%3$.3f) at RQL."
msgstr ""
"Probabilitas penerimaan (%1$.3f) di RQL (%2$.3f) <b>lebih tinggi</b> dari "
"probabilitas penerimaan diperlukan (%3$.3f) di RQL."

msgid "Acceptance Probabilities"
msgstr "Probabilitas Penerimaan"

msgid "Prop. Non-conforming"
msgstr "Non-konform Prop."

msgid "P(accept)"
msgstr "P(terima)"

msgid "OC (Operating Characteristics) Curve"
msgstr "Kurva OC (Karakteristik Operasi)"

msgid "Probability of Acceptance"
msgstr "Probabilitas Penerimaan"

msgid "AOQ (Average Outgoing Quality) Curve"
msgstr "Kurva AOQ (Kualitas Luaran Rata-rata)"

msgid "Can not calculate AOQ. Check the plan parameters."
msgstr "Tidak dapat menghitung AOQ. Periksa parameter rencana."

msgid "(Incoming) Proportion Non-conforming"
msgstr "Non-konform Proporsi (Masuk)"

msgid "Average Outgoing Quality"
msgstr "Kualitas Luaran Rata-rata"

msgid "AOQL: %.3f"
msgstr "AOQL: %.3f"

msgid "ATI (Average Total Inspection) Curve"
msgstr "Kurva ATI (Inspeksi Total Rata-rata)"

msgid "Can not calculate ATI. Check the plan parameters."
msgstr "Tidak dapat menghitung ATI. Periksa parameter rencana."

msgid "Average Total Inspection"
msgstr "Inspeksi Total Rata-rata"

msgid "ASN (Average Sample Number) Curve"
msgstr "Kurva ASN (Angka Sampel Rata-rata)"

msgid "Can not calculate ASN. Check the plan parameters."
msgstr "Tidak dapat menghitung ASN. Periksa parameter rencana."

msgid "Average Sample Number"
msgstr "Angka Sampel Rata-rata"

msgid "Generated Sampling Plan"
msgstr "Rencana Pensampelan Terhasilkan"

msgid "Acceptance probabilities at AQL and RQL"
msgstr "Probabilitas Penerimaan di AQL dan RQL"

msgid "Acceptance Probability"
msgstr "Probabilitas Penerimaan"

msgid "Rejection Probability"
msgstr "Probabilitas Penolakan"

msgid "If the number of defective items out of %1$d sampled is <= %2$d, accept the lot. Reject otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Jika jumlah item defektif dari %1$d disampel adalah <= %2$d, terima lot. "
"Tolak jika tidak."

msgid "Create Variable Plan"
msgstr "Buat Rencana Variabel"

msgid "Z.LSL = (mean - LSL) / historical standard deviation\n\nAccept lot if Z.LSL >= k, otherwise reject."
msgstr ""
"Z.LSL = (rerata - LSL) / deviasi standar historis\n"
"\n"
"Terima lot jika Z.LSL >= k, jika tidak tolak."

msgid "Variable plan generated for the current quality constraints is invalid. Modify the quality constraints."
msgstr ""
"Rencana variabel dihasilkan untuk batasan kualitas saat ini tidak valid. "
"Modifikasikan batasan kualitas."

msgid "Variable plan generated for the current quality constraints has an invalid sample size (n). Modify the quality constraints."
msgstr ""
"Rencana variabel dihasilkan untuk batasan kualitas saat ini memiliki ukuran "
"sampel (n) tidak valid. Modifikasikan batasan kualitas."

msgid "Variable plan generated for the current quality constraints has an invalid k value. Modify the quality constraints."
msgstr ""
"Rencana variabel dihasilkan untuk batasan kualitas saat ini memiliki nilai k "
"tidak valid. Modifikasikan batasan kualitas."

msgid "Accept or Reject Lot %s"
msgstr "Terima atau Tolak Lot %s"

msgid "Sample Mean"
msgstr "Rerata Sampel"

msgid "Sample Standard Deviation"
msgstr "Deviasi Standar Sampel"

msgid "Historical Standard Deviation"
msgstr "Deviasi Standar Historik"

msgid "Lower Specification Limit (LSL)"
msgstr "Batas Spesifikasi Bawah (LSL)"

msgid "Upper Specification Limit (USL)"
msgstr "Batas Spesifikasi Atas (USL)"

msgid "Z.LSL"
msgstr "Z.LSL"

msgid "Z.USL"
msgstr "Z.USL"

msgid "Sample standard deviation has to be greater than 0."
msgstr "Deviasi standar sampel harus lebih besar dari 0."

msgid "Sample mean is invalid."
msgstr "Rerata sampel tidak valid."

msgid "Can not accept or reject lot: sample size has to be greater than 1."
msgstr ""
"Tidak dapat meneriman atau menolak lot: ukuran sampel harus lebih besar dari "
"1."

msgid "Sample size has to be <b>> 1</b> if <b>both</b> LSL and USL are provided, and historical standard deviation is <b>unknown</b>."
msgstr ""
"Ukuran sampel harus <b>> 1</b> jika <b>kedua</b> LSL dan USL diberikan, dan "
"deviasi standar historik <b>tidak diketahui</b>."

msgid "<u>Decision:</u> <b>%s</b> lot."
msgstr "<u>Keputusan:</u> <b>%s</b> lot."
